{"tid":1910854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[警世］痴埋支那嘅國家（西德），武肺會爆到九彩","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:18:44.000Z","uid":282490,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7da82514a978033693238b5df484eea9f42273b","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"同支那貿易唯一可以保持順差嘅國家<br />\n<br />\n（官商）奶支成為日常<br />\n德國人將武肺當流感<br />\n<br />\n政府一面話唔駛恐慌唔駛囤貨，輕症唔駛去醫院，無病唔駛戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n超市貨架繼續日日清，市民驚奶野被隔離所以囤貨+唔敢出街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBHEroT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBHEroT.png&h=d0dadfc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://gcber.org/corona/?from=groupmessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgcber.org%2Fcorona%2F%3Ffrom%3Dgroupmessage%26isappinstalled%3D0&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=c49bf44f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gcber.org/corona/?from=groupmessage&amp;isappinstalled=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNordrhein-Westfalen州：<span style=\"color: red;\">179 cases</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNW州有乜？<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國嘅屎為總部，員工最多</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本城D&uuml;sseldorf <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBaden W&uuml;rttemberg 州：<span style=\"color: orange;\">50 cases</span><br />\nBW州有乜？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Benz 總部<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\">法蘭克福不停開國際論壇、會議，支那人至愛參加</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBayern州：<span style=\"color: orange;\">53 cases </span><br />\n巴佛利亞州有乜？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Audi 總部<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BMW 總部<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人至愛嘅德甲勁旅FC Bayern <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慕尼黑有<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全德國第二大嘅屎為分公司</span></span>，大半座大樓都係佢嘅Office <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼住意大利，最鐘意週末過去意大利玩/滑雪/行山"},{"pid":"f9f4653a462b572e4c9a9fda37d884de3f5d5d83","tid":1910854,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"一帶一路最大出口產品：武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"e12bc97a58a89addcec332b1261db8e877b3677f","tid":1910854,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42546fa7c76c10295b8b42eff16ebc5f49f0db60","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0jWtNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0jWtNs.jpg&h=a9a2dbcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾反應兩極化<br />\n左邊係：相信政府，唔怕！<br />\n另一邊係：隻病毒好撚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總體都係驚嘅多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過驚嘅都唔肯戴口罩<br />\n因為戴口罩係病左嘅人先會戴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c10150bc8c8be2e6e9a93173ead42a56f72c73","tid":1910854,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42546fa7c76c10295b8b42eff16ebc5f49f0db60","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0jWtNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=