":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a7a992042f136d90b4261ee1b0e6920aef15b80","tid":1910854,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"西德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩年代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"西德東德化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36a2303ac953c0a2b0f4f2f0c96dfa11b5502e0","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97bec4ea5b0fd99a574602f4c4321a79fdc97a42","tid":1910854,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6594eb0a07afe7ef2201907a2f8a7afc41a53840","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54143f2f537436ce2ee01c1a9145da900dafd04","tid":1910854,"uid":332635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"一早比支那掃走左d口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"掃唔掃都唔會戴<br />\n因為佢地深信「<span style=\"color: orange;\">病左先會戴口罩</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"其實係咩邏輯，病咗就去醫院啦<br />\n唔通愛支病都淨係帶個口罩就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"德國醫生：輕症唔好去醫院"},{"pid":"421ffac220be4055cdca0c47ececaf3fd01de79c","tid":1910854,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（又稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續蔓延，德國拒絕承認世界衛生組織（WHO，世衛）總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）的講法，<span style=\"color: violet;\">德國衛生部自行宣布，新冠肺炎已成為「全球瘟疫大流行」（worldwide pandemic）。<br />\n</span><br />\n【歐洲疫情分佈】意大利死亡高於伊朗 全國停課<br />\n<br />\n英國政府拒每日公布疫情捱批<br />\n<br />\n德國衛生部長施潘（Jens Spahn）周三稱，新冠肺炎疫情已成全球大流行，德國疫情仍未達到巔峰，強調人類的健康比經濟利益重要。世衛連日來一直堅稱疫情未構成全球大流行。<br />\n<br />\n施潘表示：「無人真的知道疫情何時達到最高峰，但說出這將會發生十分重要，讓我們都能作好準備。在目前形勢，最緊要保持冷靜，大家團結，並準備好互相信任，即使身處壓力中。」<br />\n<br />\n美國加州死者曾坐遊輪 21人疑染病<br />\n<br />\n【美國疫情分佈】紐約激增10確診 加州首死緊急狀態<br />\n<br />\n疫情持續在德國擴散，確診個案增至逾250宗，全國16個州有15個已失守，近半患者來自重災區北萊茵－威斯特伐利亞州（North Rhine-Westphalia）。<br />\n<br />\n出於抗疫考慮，德國政府已在周三宣布，禁止出口口罩、手套等醫療防護用品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2581807?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2581807%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=c19d2fd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2581807?r=mcsdfb2</a>"}]}